name: Bow to Your Masters
description:
Bow to the masters of capitalism who run the world. Bow for toys, bow for clothes, bow for the hot tech of the second, bow, bow, bow. Selling yourself, your time, your money, your health all for what?

Nothing of substance, nothing of importance. Don't sell yourself. Stay true to you. Stay true to your vision.

Collage by @dehiscenceart
Minted for Art Basel Miami Beach, December, 2021
JPG 5400px X 7400px
